   experimental data were correlated using the NRTL, UNIQUAC and Modified
   UNIFAC (Do) models. Additionally, the experimental measurements of
   densities and sound velocities were measured for binary systems (water
   or methanol or ethanol (1) + 1,3-propanediol (2)) at atmospheric
   pressure and at (283.15, 293.15, 303.15 and 313.15)K. The
