   Zaatar, Y.; Khoury, A., Univ Libanaise, Fac Sci 2, Appl Phys Lab, Jdeidet El Metn 90656, Lebanon.}},
DOI = {{10.1016/j.ijhydene.2010.04.107}},
ISSN = {{0360-3199}},
EISSN = {{1879-3487}},
Keywords = {{Alumina; Cobalt; Electrophoretic deposition; Hydrolysis; Sodium
